channel.title: Strictly Come Dancing
channel.desc: Nerves are mounting in the ballroom for our remaining couples as they await the outcome of the public vote. Our professionals are joined by the Band of the Royal Air Force Regiment for a beautiful performance to mark Remembrance Sunday, and there's music from James Morrison. As two more couples prepare to dance off, who will make it through to another weekend on Strictly?
